          Historique des incidents
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-2">
                Date
              </th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2">
                Type
              </th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2">
                Gravité
              </th>
              <th class="px-4 py-2">
                Description
              </th>
